      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That \"temporary state\" thing is just a lie people tell to feel better. I don't believe in \"light at the end of the tunnel\" or some better version of life waiting for me. Everything is just entropy and nothingness. If everything is fundamentally empty, why am I even fighting so hard to stay in this room? It feels like I'm just dragging weight through sand for no reason.",
